{"tid":1089181,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"美聯太子女黃靜怡疑首次置業入市   半億購入跑馬地樂天峯","createTime":"2019-04-02T14:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T09:28:49.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"17397f68e49b1890d24470e3cec4afdb34c70746","tid":1089181,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190402/large/1554214327_43a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190402%2Flarge%2F1554214327_43a8.jpg&h=bd18579e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地產市道暢旺，連帶代理收入水漲船高。美聯集團(1200)主席黃建業女兒、集團副主席黃靜怡，新近豪花半億元買樓。土地註冊處資料顯示，跑馬地樂天峯一個中層B室實用面積1,280方呎三房單位，上月登記以5,000萬元易手，呎價39,063元，買家為黃靜怡(WONG CHING YI ANGELA)，與美聯集團副主席同名。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，黃靜怡是次入市只需支付最低4.25%釐印費，涉資212.5萬元，意味屬首置身份。根據美聯2017年年報顯示，黃靜怡年薪逾1,500萬元。美聯集團上周公佈業績，去年少賺七成，純利5,813萬元，每股盈利8.1仙，不派末期息。<br />\n<br />\n座落樂活道12號的樂天峯是由老牌地產商合和（0054）興建，2010年落成，單位總數76伙。"},{"pid":"15a635d764da32a98f2ce9bbe98b54fd50341042","tid":1089181,"uid":190540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc6f1ed9374fb08ee4a1b9681751614c44476deb","tid":1089181,"uid":146435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"有冇幫襯自己公司買"},{"pid":"8bce8752419a23b513003e18a2b86b878aa3d093","tid":1089181,"uid":105906,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T14:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dVWxc2E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdVWxc2E.png&h=4355cfc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接火捧<br />\n有排受"},{"pid":"b6d96e03b9ac367876ed1ba881a155911756d7f9","tid":1089181,"uid":228794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"AA左手交右手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf65b7dd58f1ae724777f34362468386fa79fc